00:08:16.896 --> 00:08:17.366 A:middle
Property.

00:08:17.626 --> 00:08:21.466 A:middle
With that in place, the only

00:08:21.466 --> 00:08:22.396 A:middle
thing left to do in our

00:08:22.396 --> 00:08:24.146 A:middle
definition of custom responses

00:08:25.206 --> 00:08:26.556 A:middle
is to define the template.

00:08:26.956 --> 00:08:28.966 A:middle
The template is what is spoken

00:08:28.966 --> 00:08:29.736 A:middle
out by Siri.

00:08:31.036 --> 00:08:32.895 A:middle
So, when we look at the template

00:08:32.946 --> 00:08:34.446 A:middle
section of our Intent Definition

00:08:34.446 --> 00:08:37.236 A:middle
File, now I'm going to add my

00:08:37.236 --> 00:08:38.135 A:middle
