00:09:37.006 --> 00:09:39.746 A:middle
comprises of two steps: confirm

00:09:40.246 --> 00:09:40.746 A:middle
and handle.

00:09:42.316 --> 00:09:44.906 A:middle
In confirmation, we are asked

00:09:44.906 --> 00:09:46.836 A:middle
