00:09:46.836 --> 00:09:48.196 A:middle
this intent at this time.

00:09:49.306 --> 00:09:51.526 A:middle
So, we'll first find out whether

00:09:51.526 --> 00:09:53.116 A:middle
the soup the user has requested

00:09:53.396 --> 00:09:54.806 A:middle
is in our menu.

00:09:56.286 --> 00:09:57.826 A:middle
If it is, we'll let the system

00:09:57.826 --> 00:09:59.456 A:middle
know that we are ready to place

00:09:59.456 --> 00:09:59.796 A:middle
the order.

00:10:00.976 --> 00:10:02.936 A:middle
But this is our chance to also

00:10:02.936 --> 00:10:04.656 A:middle
check that the soup is available

